{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d45bbb159f","title":"对范仲渣两首词的评注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4a589e05dc","index":0,"year":1957,"month":8,"day":1,"articleId":"d45bbb159f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"5c23ae011a","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"范仲流（989-1052），字希文，苏州吴县（今吴县市）人，北宋政治家、文学家。"},{"id":"e023d07e3b","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李钠，1940年生，毛泽东之女。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bea406fcd1","type":"title","text":"对范仲流两首词的评注","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"5c23ae011a","type":"paragraph","text":"苏幕遮","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"e023d07e3b","type":"paragraph","text":"碧云天，黄叶地，秋色连波，波上寒烟翠。山映斜阳天接水，芳草无情，更在斜阳外。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"9a82d24841","type":"paragraph","text":"路乡魂，追旅思，夜夜除非，好梦留人睡。明月楼高休独倚。酒入慈肠，化作相思泪。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"8a3e4cdf89","type":"paragraph","text":"渔家傲","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"5333833bf7","type":"paragraph","text":"塞下秋来风景异，衡阳雁去无留意。四面边声连角起。干哺里，长烟落日孤城闭。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"883743e975","type":"paragraph","text":"冲酒一杯家万里，燕然未勒归无计。芜管悠悠霜满地。人不麻，将军白发征夫泪。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"197d909b92","type":"paragraph","text":"词有婉约、豪放两派，各有兴会，应当兼读。读婉约派久了，央倦了，要改读豪放派。豪放派读久了，文庆倦了，应当改读婉约派。我的兴趣偏于豪放，不废婉约。婉约派中有许多意境苍凉而又优美的词。范仲庵的上两首，介于婉约与豪放两派之间，可算中间派吧；但基本上仍属婉约，既苍凉又优美，便人不庆读。婉约派中的一味儿女情长，豪放派中的一味铜琶铁板，读久了，都令人庆借的。人的心情是复杂的，有所偏但仍是复杂的。所谓复杂，就是对立统一。人的心情，经常有对立的成分，不是单一的，是可以分析的。词的婉约、豪放两派，在一个人读起来，有时喜欢前者，有时喜欢后者，就是一例。睡不着，晾范词，写了这些。江青看后，给李诚看一看。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"},{"id":"cb86b2b5d9","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年八月一日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f"}],"page":{"id":"7c40e85929","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d45bbb159f","start":198,"end":199}}}},"__N_SSG":true}